Provides: mpd-client
Description: A complete GTK2 client for MPD 
 A complete GTK2 client for MPD (Music Player Daemon)
 The interface used to browse the library is inspired by Rhythmbox but Ario
 aims to be much lighter and faster.
 URL: http://ario-player.sourceforge.net/
